About Us
Prime 88 embodies the belief that fine steaks and wine are not limited to the city. Our "cut above" philosophy is inspired by the timeless tradition of classic steakhouses, where every dining experience is unforgettable. Whether you choose to dine in our intimate dining room, lively bar or relaxing patio, our exceptional food and service are sure to exceed your expectations.
Prime 88 features an inviting outdoor patio, and a lively bar. Our main dining area features comfortable seating options, a private dining area and is anchored by our unique wine display room. As an independent and local business, we are committed to providing the best possible experience to our guests and our community.
